    "body": "if we set UDP to ENR, most of our peers are inbound\r\n- this branch\r\n<img width=\"1304\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 08 21\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211140722-6fa65e48-15ac-4945-8274-a709f7383e30.png\">\r\n\r\n- unstable\r\n<img width=\"1269\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 08 52\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211140741-012c5352-fef3-410c-8ed7-f8dac712b2da.png\">\r\n\r\nwe received/sent ways more goodbye requests from/to peers\r\n- this branch\r\n<img width=\"1264\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 10 40\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211140796-72506636-406e-4052-a466-88f26acf173f.png\">\r\n<img width=\"1270\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 11 01\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211140809-8d394865-6586-46b7-9c03-6821c526e7d6.png\">\r\n\r\n- unstable\r\n<img width=\"1273\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 11 47\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211140836-d09f79b1-7948-4413-b0b9-06964aa9d5a6.png\">\r\n<img width=\"1275\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 13 58\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211140925-7ef817ae-1817-4e49-a702-b8a5d1005588.png\">\r\n\r\nlodestar tends to switch peers a lot with this branch, this is peer connection length\r\n- this branch\r\n<img width=\"1287\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 33 32\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211141560-a806387d-7bf3-4024-8de8-42c929233b3c.png\">\r\n\r\n- unstable\r\n<img width=\"1302\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 33 59\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211141590-24f41bd4-1fb6-422f-adf6-3e1f947bea66.png\">\r\n\r\nalthough it switches peers a lot, the long lived subnet is worse\r\n- this branch\r\n<img width=\"1293\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 37 09\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211141754-c410e552-0732-4d83-868b-005d5fbe67ca.png\">\r\n\r\n- unstable\r\n<img width=\"1274\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 37 46\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211141801-bdc38b02-f56b-4c49-b58d-e907e846d52b.png\">\r\n\r\nnumber of peers are usually 55 instead of 50 as in unstable\r\n- this branch\r\n<img width=\"1275\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 42 39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211141981-ead00ec8-0fec-49a1-ac6d-7b65279fe41d.png\">\r\n\r\n- unstable\r\n<img width=\"1280\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-07 at 15 43 11\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/211141996-0c0344fa-334c-4959-a040-acdc2202adb1.png\">\r\n\r\nthere's really an issue of peer management at lodestar side",
