    "body": "The memory leak issue also happens with unstable/stable (v1.3.0). Setting udp to enr makes it happen consistently\r\n\r\nThis is from stable (v1.3.0) 1k validators:\r\n<img width=\"802\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-13 at 09 34 59\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/212223976-efd1734b-edf7-4f53-8256-fe1b883aa2a1.png\">\r\n\r\nThis really correlate to `beacon_blocks_by_range`, `beacon_blocks_by_root`, `status` incoming requests\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1276\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-13 at 09 38 40\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/212224523-aca125a4-a49a-496d-bb68-839f77fe596f.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1273\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-13 at 09 38 53\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/212224559-cbd93c99-9f56-4020-b71e-2bb0dee0464d.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1292\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-01-13 at 09 39 04\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/212224584-208d5e05-cc13-43be-8bc3-09eb700a07b4.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\nI notice that it does not happen with other stable nodes. \r\n",
